text:

Published October 25th, 2015 - 12:16 GMT via SyndiGate.info Rate Article: Carole Samaha reveals the first pictures of her newborn Tala. (YouTube) Follow > Click here to add Carole Samaha as an alert Click here to remove the Carole Samaha alert Disable alert for Carole Samaha , Click here to add Facebook as an alert Click here to remove the Facebook alert Disable alert for Facebook 
OK. We're experiencing cuteness overdose and it's all Carole Samaha's fault. 
Our hearts were officially melted soon as we watched the Lebanese singer's new music video "Tala," which she had dedicated to her firstborn and revealed the first photos of her bundle of joy . 
Tala's adorable smile, cotton-soft cheeks and gorgeous blue eyes were enough reasons to have the video on replay over the weekend. 
"Tala the video" consisted of a photo collage of Carole, Tala and her new toys and accessories. 
Photo: Facebook.
